==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Transportation
<hw>Trans`por*ta"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>transportatio</ets>: cf. F. <ets>transportation</ets>.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of transporting, or the state of being
transported; carriage from one place to another; removal;
conveyance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To provide a vessel for their <qex>transportation</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Sir H. Wotton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Transport; ecstasy.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
<rj><au>South.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Transported</ent>⟦br⟧
